---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-hero-title">About Me & This Website</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-description">Discover the heart behind the code and the soul behind this portfolio</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-card">
        <h2 class="about-card-title">Who I Am</h2>

        <div class="image-content-wrapper left">
          <div class="image-container">
            <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Tanniru Jagadeesh Kumar" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
          </div>
          <div class="image-content">
            <div class="about-content">
              <p>Hi, I'm Jagadeesh — a quiet soul with a heart that feels deeply and a mind that dreams big. I believe the world changes not through loud voices, but through gentle hands that build, heal, and uplift. Technology, to me, is not just about code — it's about crafting experiences that make people feel seen, understood, and valued.</p>

              <p>I stepped into the world of programming in 2023, not because I wanted to prove something, but because I wanted to <span class="highlight">create something meaningful</span>. Every line of code I write carries a piece of my heart — whether it's a website for a small business owner chasing their dream, or a tool that makes someone's day a little easier.</p>

              <p>I'm the kind of person who pauses to help, who listens more than I speak, and who finds joy in the success of others. My friends say I wear my heart on my sleeve, and I think that's okay. In a world that often rewards toughness, I choose kindness — not as a weakness, but as my greatest strength.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="quote">
            <p class="quote-text">"Be the reason someone believes in the goodness of people. Kindness costs nothing, but it means everything."</p>
            <p class="quote-author">— Jagadeesh's Belief</p>
          </div>

          <p>Beyond the screen, I find peace in the simple things — a quiet evening walk, the warmth of a genuine conversation, the laughter of friends, and the comfort of knowing I made someone's day a little brighter. I believe that true strength lies not in how much you can endure alone, but in how much love you can give to others.</p>

          <p>I don't claim to have all the answers, and I'm not trying to be perfect. I'm just someone who shows up every day with an open heart, a willingness to learn, and a quiet determination to leave this world a little kinder than I found it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">3+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years of Learning</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">20+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Projects Built</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">10+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Technologies</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">∞</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Heartfelt Moments</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-card">
        <h2 class="about-card-title">The Journey So Far</h2>
        <div class="milestone-timeline">
          <div class="milestone-item">
            <div class="milestone-year">2023</div>
            <div class="milestone-title">A New Beginning</div>
            <div class="milestone-description">Took the first step into the world of code — not for fame, but for the joy of creating. Every mistake was a lesson, every small win a celebration.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone-item">
            <div class="milestone-year">2024</div>
            <div class="milestone-title">Building Dreams</div>
            <div class="milestone-description">Started helping small businesses and individuals bring their visions to life. Each project was more than a contract — it was a story I got to be part of.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone-item">
            <div class="milestone-year">2025</div>
            <div class="milestone-title">Growing Together</div>
            <div class="milestone-description">Joined a team of incredible people, learning that the best code is written not by individuals, but by communities who care about each other.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone-item">
            <div class="milestone-year">2026</div>
            <div class="milestone-title">Giving Back</div>
            <div class="milestone-description">Contributing to open-source and sharing what I've learned. Because the best thing you can do with knowledge is pass it on to someone who needs it.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-card">
        <h2 class="about-card-title">About This Website</h2>

        <div class="image-content-wrapper right">
          <div class="image-container">
            <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Tanniru Jagadeesh Kumar" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
          </div>
          <div class="image-content">
            <div class="about-content">
              <p>This little corner of the internet is more than just a portfolio — it's a <span class="highlight">piece of my heart</span>, carefully woven into every pixel and every word. I built it not to impress, but to connect — to share my journey, my thoughts, and the things I've created along the way.</p>

              <p>Everything you see here was crafted with intention and care. I believe that even the smallest details matter — because someone out there will notice, and that someone might just feel a little more inspired to start their own journey.</p>

              <p>If something here resonates with you, if a single line makes you smile or think or feel — then I've done what I set out to do. This website is my way of saying: <span class="highlight">you're not alone</span>, and the world is full of people who care.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="quote">
            <p class="quote-text">"The best websites aren't built with perfect code — they're built with intention, heart, and a genuine desire to make someone's day better."</p>
            <p class="quote-author">— Jagadeesh</p>
          </div>

          <p>Thank you for being here. Whether you're a fellow creator, a friend, or someone just passing through — I hope you find something here that speaks to you. And if you'd like to say hello, I'd love to hear from you.</p>

          <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--gold);">With warmth,<br><strong>Jagadeesh</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
